@startuml HealSense_Alert_System
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml
LAYOUT_TOP_DOWN()
title HealSense: Alert Detection and Management System

package "Alert Detection" as detection {
    component "Vital Signs Monitor\n(Real-time Stream)" as monitor
    component "ML Risk Scorer" as ml_scorer
    component "Threshold Checker\n(Clinical Limits)" as threshold_checker
    component "Alert Condition Evaluator" as evaluator
}

package "Alert Classification" as classification {
    component "Severity Classifier\nLOW | MEDIUM | HIGH | CRITICAL" as severity
    component "Alert Type Mapper\n(HIGH_HR, LOW_SPO2, etc.)" as alerttype
    component "Patient Risk Context\n(Medical history)" as context
}

package "Alert Database & State" as dbstate {
    component "Alert Record Creator\n(persistent storage)" as dbcreator
    component "Alert State Manager\n(ACTIVE, ACKNOWLEDGED, RESOLVED)" as statemanager
    component "Alert History & Audit" as history
}

package "Alert Escalation" as escalation {
    component "Auto-Escalation Rules\n(CRITICAL → Emergency)" as autorules
    component "Emergency Contact Resolver\n(Doctor, family)" as contacts
    component "Escalation Workflow\n(SMS → Call → EMS)" as workflow
}

package "Notification Dispatch" as notification {
    component "Mobile Push\n(Firebase FCM)" as fcm
    component "WebSocket Real-time\n(Live stream)" as websocket
    component "Email Notification" as email
    component "SMS Alerts\n(Critical only)" as sms
    component "In-App Notification" as inapp
}

package "Alert Management UI" as management {
    component "Mobile App Alert View" as mobile_view
    component "Provider Dashboard\nAlert List" as provider_list
    component "Alert Detail & Actions" as detail
    component "Acknowledge Interface" as acknowledge
    component "Dismiss Interface" as dismiss
}

package "User Actions" as actions {
    component "Acknowledge Alert\n(Mark reviewed)" as user_ack
    component "Dismiss Alert\n(False positive)" as user_dismiss
    component "Resolve Alert\n(Issue resolved)" as user_resolve
    component "Add Resolution Notes" as user_notes
}

monitor --> ml_scorer
ml_scorer --> threshold_checker
threshold_checker --> evaluator

evaluator --> severity
severity --> alerttype
alerttype --> context

context --> dbcreator
dbcreator --> statemanager
statemanager --> history

evaluator --> autorules
autorules --> contacts
contacts --> workflow

workflow --> fcm
fcm --> notification
workflow --> websocket
websocket --> notification
notification --> email
notification --> sms
notification --> inapp

fcm --> mobile_view
websocket --> mobile_view
websocket --> provider_list
provider_list --> detail

mobile_view --> acknowledge
provider_list --> acknowledge
mobile_view --> dismiss
provider_list --> dismiss
detail --> acknowledge
detail --> dismiss
detail --> user_notes

acknowledge --> user_ack
dismiss --> user_dismiss
user_notes --> user_resolve

note right of severity
ALERT SEVERITY LEVELS:
LOW: Minor deviation
  (HR: 55-65 bpm)
  Action: Monitor

MEDIUM: Notable concern
  (HR: 50-55 bpm)
  Action: Notice provider

HIGH: Significant issue  
  (HR: 40-50 bpm)
  Action: Provider alert

CRITICAL: Emergency
  (HR: <40 or >130 bpm)
  Action: Auto-escalate
end note

note right of evaluator
ALERT CONDITIONS:
- HR: <50 or >120 (WARNING)
        <40 or >130 (CRITICAL)
- SpO2: <92% (WARNING)
          <90% (CRITICAL)
- Temp: >38.5°C (WARNING)
          >40°C (CRITICAL)
- BP: SysBP >140 (WARNING)
       SysBP >180 (CRITICAL)
- RR: <8 or >30 (CRITICAL)
end note

note right of statemanager
ALERT STATES:
ACTIVE
  → ACKNOWLEDGED (provider reviews)
  → DISMISSED (false alert)
  
ACKNOWLEDGED
  → RESOLVED (issue handled)
  
RESOLVED
  → ARCHIVED (historical)
end note

note right of workflow
ESCALATION WORKFLOW:
If CRITICAL for 5 mins:
1. Auto-call hospital
2. SMS to emergency contact
3. Call emergency contact
4. Activate EMS if no response
end note

@enduml
